cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.DS, cs.NE 

The paper presents an end-to-end deep learning framework for early classification of time series data, which involves feature learning and dynamic truncation. This work is related to machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), data structures and algorithms (cs.DS), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
